track_notes: This trailhead is just a few hundred yards away from the Mt. Pleasant trailhead on Wiggins Road

Track includes round trip to Cole Mtn, Bald Knob and back to start. Start at (37.75681, -79.21597). This trailhead is accessible by motor vehicle only during hunting season. Hike trail 3226 to AT at Cowcamp Gap to either or both summits.
